history.content: I notice upper div CS classes have seats reserved only until Saturday, Jan 8th, while Phase 2 ends after Jan 9th and Adjustment starts on Monday, Jan 10th. For instance reserved seats for CS 160 expired after Jan 8th while reserved seats for EECS 16B expired after Jan 9th. This seems to deviate from the EECS enrollment policy which said only CS/EECS major can enroll in seats in upper division CS classes during Phase 2. Does this mean waitlist re-ordering would happen on Jan 8th in stead of Jan 9th, the last day of Phase 2?
history.subject: CS Seats not reserved untill Adjustment
